Welcome Letter

Dear Guest,

We are delighted to welcome you to Hilton Dubai Jumeirah and Hilton Dubai The Walk. Whether you are here for business or leisure, our dedicated team is ready to make your stay truly exceptional.

Following the reopening of Hilton Dubai Jumeirah, we are excited to share that Taliahs Caf has now opened in the lobby, offering the perfect selection of coffee and ptisserie delights. In addition, our signature restaurants, Villa Verona and Trader Vics JBR, are ready to welcome you with their refreshed menus, crafted to bring you new flavors and experiences.

From our prime location on Jumeirah Beach to our diverse dining venues, wellness facilities, and personalized services, everything has been designed with your comfort in mind. Should you need any assistance before or during your stay, please do not hesitate to reach out to our teamwe are here for you every step of the way.

We look forward to creating memorable moments with you.

Jean Sebastien Kling

Cluster General Manager

Parking & Valet Service

Valet Service

Available 24/7 for all in-house guests. Simply hand your keys to our valet team at the entrance.

Parking Details

Complimentary on-site parking is available for guests.

Both self-parking and valet parking options are provided.

Important Information

Arrival & Departure

Our Front Desk Team is here to welcome you and ensure a smooth process for check-in at 3:00 PM and check-out at 12:00 PM, while catering to your preferences throughout your stay.

Please note:

To facilitate a smooth check-in, please present the credit or debit card used to secure your booking. If this card will not be available, kindly inform us in advance so we can assist with alternative payment arrangements.

In the absence of the original card, payment may be processed on another card at check-in, with the initial charge subsequently refunded.
